{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create an exact pixel-perfect HTML and CSS layout for a Shopify product section.
    
    STRICT REQUIREMENTS:
    - Do NOT change layout, spacing, or structure.
    - Match the design EXACTLY as described.
    
    LAYOUT:
    - A light grey background container (#f3f3f3)
    - Inside it, there are 2 rows
    - Each row uses a 3-column layout:
      1. Left icon
      2. Center text (center aligned, stacked vertically)
      3. Right icon
    
    ROW 1:
    - Left: circular outline icon with a right arrow inside (thin red stroke)
    - Center text (stacked, centered):
      Easy
      15
      Day
      Return
    - Right: vertical oval outline icon with a sparkle/star inside (thin red stroke)
    
    ROW 2:
    - Left: rounded square outline icon with number "6" inside
    - Center text (stacked):
      6-Month
      Warranty
    - Right: vertical oval outline icon with "925" inside
    
    STYLE:
    - Icon stroke color: muted red (#b94a55)
    - Thin outline stroke (not filled)
    - Icons must be SVG, not emoji or images
    - Text color: dark grey (#444)
    - Font: clean sans-serif (like Arial)
    - Large font size (~36–40px)
    - Perfect vertical alignment
    - Even spacing between rows (~80–100px)
    - Icons centered vertically with text
    
    IMPORTANT:
    - Do NOT use flex incorrectly — use grid for 3-column alignment
    - Do NOT stack icons or misalign them
    - Do NOT approximate icons — create clean SVG line icons
    
    OUTPUT:
    - Only HTML + CSS
    - No explanation
    - Clean, production-ready code, Create a pixel-perfect HTML and CSS component that exactly matches the provided UI design.
    
    STRICT INSTRUCTIONS:
    - Do NOT change layout, spacing, alignment, or proportions.
    - The output must visually match the design exactly.
    - No approximations.
    
    LAYOUT:
    - A full-width light grey background (#f3f3f3)
    - Inside it, a 2-column grid layout
    - 2 rows total (4 items)
    
    GRID STRUCTURE:
    Row 1:
      Left: Icon + "Easy 15 Day Return"
      Right: Icon + "Lifetime Plating"
    
    Row 2:
      Left: Icon + "6-Month Warranty"
      Right: Icon + "Fine 925 Silver"
    
    EACH ITEM:
    - Horizontal layout (icon on left, text on right)
    - Vertically centered alignment
    - Equal spacing between icon and text
    - Consistent spacing between grid items
    
    ICONS (VERY IMPORTANT):
    - Use inline SVG (no images, no emojis)
    - Thin stroke line icons
    - Color: muted red (#b94a55)
    - Style: minimal outline icons
    - Icons required:
      1. Circular arrow box icon (return symbol)
      2. Ring icon (for lifetime plating)
      3. Warranty badge with "6"
      4. Circular "925" silver stamp
    
    TYPOGRAPHY:
    - Font: clean sans-serif (Arial or similar)
    - Color: dark grey (#444)
    - Font size: medium (~18–20px)
    - Font weight: normal (not bold)
    
    SPACING:
    - Balanced padding inside container (around 40–60px)
    - Equal gap between columns
    - Equal vertical spacing between rows
    
    TECHNICAL:
    - Use CSS Grid for layout (NOT flex for main structure)
    - Use flex ONLY for icon + text alignment inside each item
    - Ensure pixel-perfect alignment and spacing
    
    OUTPUT:
    - Only HTML and CSS
    - No explanation
    - Clean, production-ready code, Design a mobile-friendly feature highlights section for an eCommerce jewelry website.
    
    The section should display 4 key benefits in a 2x2 grid layout (two items per row).
    
    Each item must include:
    
    A minimal line-style icon inside a circular outline
    A short label text next to the icon
    
    The 4 items are:
    
    Easy 15 Day Return
    Lifetime Plating
    6-Month Warranty
    Fine 925 Silver
    
    Design requirements:
    
    Clean, minimal, modern UI
    Use a light gray background (#f5f5f5 or similar)
    Icons and accent color should be soft red / maroon tone
    Text should be dark gray, medium weight
    Maintain good spacing and padding for mobile screens
    Icons should be aligned left with text on the right
    Each row should have equal spacing between items
    Ensure readability and touch-friendly spacing
    
    Mobile optimization:
    
    Responsive layout (stack into 2 columns on small screens)
    Proper padding (16px–20px)
    Font size around 14–16px
    
    Style should feel premium, elegant, and jewelry-brand appropriate.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-features-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: {{ block.settings.desktop_width_percent }}%;
    max-width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding }}px;
  }

  .ai-features-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap }}px;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-feature-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: {{ block.settings.icon_text_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-feature-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_circle_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_circle_size }}px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: {{ block.settings.circle_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-feature-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    stroke: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: {{ block.settings.icon_stroke_width }};
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  .ai-feature-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.font_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.font_weight }};
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-features-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.mobile_padding }}px;
    }

    .ai-features-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      gap: {{ block.settings.mobile_grid_gap }}px;
    }

    .ai-feature-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.mobile_font_size }}px;
    }

    .ai-feature-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.mobile_icon_circle_size }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.mobile_icon_circle_size }}px;
    }

    .ai-feature-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
      width: {{ block.settings.mobile_icon_size }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.mobile_icon_size }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-features-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-features-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-feature-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-feature-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M3 9h18v10a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V9z"/>
          <path d="M3 9V7a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v2"/>
          <path d="M9 5V3"/>
          <path d="M15 5V3"/>
          <path d="M9 15l2 2 4-4"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="ai-feature-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.feature_1 }}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="ai-feature-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-feature-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="2"/>
          <path d="M12 10c-3.5 0-6 2-6 4.5V16h12v-1.5c0-2.5-2.5-4.5-6-4.5z"/>
          <path d="M6 14.5c0-1.5 1-2.8 2.5-3.5"/>
          <path d="M18 14.5c0-1.5-1-2.8-2.5-3.5"/>
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="ai-feature-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.feature_2 }}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="ai-feature-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-feature-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M12 2L4 6v6c0 5.5 3.8 10.7 8 12 4.2-1.3 8-6.5 8-12V6l-8-4z"/>
          <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="ai-feature-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.feature_3 }}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="ai-feature-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-feature-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
          <path d="M8 10.5v3h1.5v-3H8z M10.5 10.5v3H12v-3h-1.5z M13 10.5v3h1.5l1.5-3v3"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="ai-feature-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.feature_4 }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Feature highlights",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Features"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "feature_1",
      "label": "Feature 1",
      "default": "Easy 15 Day Return"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "feature_2",
      "label": "Feature 2",
      "default": "Lifetime Plating"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "feature_3",
      "label": "Feature 3",
      "default": "6-Month Warranty"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
